Description: THIS PROJECT WILL PROVIDE THE FOLLOWING: (1)FULFILL COMMITMENTS IN THE 2015 SUISUN MARSH PRESERVATION AGREEMENT; (2) MAINTAIN WATER QUALITY AND QUANTITY AND IMPROVE WETLAND HABITAT IN SUISUN MARSH TO MITIGATE THE ADVERSE EFFECTS ON THE MARSH OF THE CENTRAL VALLEY PROJECT AND A PORTION OF THE ADVERSE EFFECTS OF THE UPSTREAM DIVERSIONS; AND (3) IMPROVE MARSH WILDLIFE HABITAT TO THE EXTENT THAT SUCH IMPROVEMENTS IS COMPATIBLE WITH OTHER CVP AND STATE WATER PROJECT PURPOSES.
